.com/leon0399/llame/issues/118), and\\n+  [#119](https://github.com/leon0399/llame/issues/119) cover remaining Run budget,\\n+  event-delivery, and retention work.\\n+- Fine-grained tool policy and approvals, user-scoped MCP/OAuth, user BYOK, and\\n+  write-capable remote tools need separate slices.\\n+\\n+Deferred means unsequenced, not closed.\\n+\\n+## Unsequenced horizons\\n+\\n+These remain in [VISION.md](VISION.md) until promoted into concrete milestones:\\n+\\n+- workspaces and Artifacts;\\n+- Agent Profiles, child Chats/Runs, and external coding harnesses;\\n+- Apps, workflows, email/calendar connectors, and messaging channels;\\n+- enrolled Workers and sandbox execution;\\n+- shared knowledge and enterprise information-flow controls; and\\n+- governed self-improvement and self-maintenance.\\n*** End Patch\";\ntext(await tools.apply_patch(patch));\n",
